00:36:12,799 --> 00:36:18,060
also in the American, I think, by extension, of what our leaders are supposed to be like,

566
00:36:18,240 --> 00:36:21,421
what government is supposed to be like, what the country is supposed to be like.

567
00:36:21,461 --> 00:36:24,082
We're supposed to live in a world of round tables and nights.

568
00:36:24,422 --> 00:36:25,543
And we like to believe that we do.

569
00:36:26,430 --> 00:36:27,172
but we often don't.

